metadata.name: I Spy Waldo #1
metadata.description: I Spy Waldo is a first-of-its-kind NFT linked directly with an interactive play to earn game map that gives you the chance to earn free NFTs, coins, and other rewards! Step into a beautifully rendered 3D landscape of Wallys World with 1,111 uniquely generated characters and 1,111 uniquely generated I Spy Waldo Maps , packed full of characters from the world of I Spy Waldo. NFTs will boast 200+ traits between characters and maps. Holding the matching I Spy Waldo along with the I Spy Map will earn you access to our VIP Waldo Club. Are you ready to play I Spy Waldo on Opensea?
